on.aspx?id=10 |work=bluemoon-mcfc.co.uk |accessdate=25 February 2013}}</ref>\n|First Division\n|34||7||1||0|| || ||35||7\n|-\n|[[1901\u201302 Manchester City F.C. season|1901\u201302]]\n|First Division\n|33||8||3||0|| || ||36||8\n|-\n|[[1902\u201303 Manchester City F.C. season|1902\u201303]]\n|Second Division\n|34||7||1||0|| || ||35||7\n|-\n|[[1903\u201304 Manchester City F.C. season|1903\u201304]]<ref>{{cite web |title=MCFC Matches |url=http://www.bluemoon-mcfc.co.uk/History/Matches/Season.aspx?id=13 |work=bluemoon-mcfc.co.uk |accessdate=25 February 2013}}</ref>\n|First Division\n|34||11||6||2|| || ||40||13\n|-\n|[[1904\u201305 Manchester City F.C. season|1904\u201305]]<ref>{{citation |title=MCFC Matches |url=http://www.bluemoon-mcfc.co.uk/History/Matches/Season.aspx?id=14 |publisher=bluemoon-mcfc.co.uk |accessdate=25 February 2013}}</ref>\n|First Division\n|33||8||2||1|| || ||35||9\n|-\n|[[1905\u201306 Manchester City F.C. season|1905\u201306]]<ref>{{citation |title=MCFC Matches |url=http://www.bluemoon-mcfc.co.uk/History/Matches/Season.aspx?id=15 |publisher=bluemoon-mcfc.co.uk |accessdate=25 February 2013}}</ref>\n|First Division\n| || || || || || || ||\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n!339!!129!!19!!4!!4!!1!!362!!134\n|-\n|rowspan=\"12\"|[[Manchester United F.C.|Manchester United]]\n|[[1906\u201307 Manchester United F.C. season|1906\u201307]]<ref name=\"William Henry Meredith\">{{cite web|title=William Henry Meredith|url=http://www.mufcinfo.com/manupag/a-z_player_archive/a-z_player_archive_pages/meredith_william.html|work=mufcinfo.com|accessdate=15 February 2013}}</ref>\n|First Division\n|16||5||2||0||0||0||18||5\n|-\n|[[1907\u201308 Manchester United F.C. season|1907\u201308]]<ref name=\"William Henry Meredith\"/>\n|First Division\n|37||10||4||0||2||1||43||11\n|-\n|[[1908\u201309 Manchester United F.C. season|1908\u201309]]<ref name=\"William Henry Meredith\"/>\n|First Division\n|34||0||4||0||0||0||38||0\n|-\n|[[1909\u201310 Manchester United F.C. season|1909\u201310